<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>i3 FAQ - Individual question feed</title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/questions/</link><description>Frequently asked questions and answers about the i3 window manager</description><atom:link href="http://faq.i3wm.org/feeds/question/6575/" rel="self"></atom:link><language>en</language><copyright>Copyright i3, 2012</copyright><lastBuildDate>Sun, 13 Sep 2015 16:31:34 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>Change floating window move step</title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/6575/change-floating-window-move-step/</link><description> I'd like to increase step of moving floating windows ($mod+shift+[ j k l ; ]), is there a way to do it without recompiling i3?</description><pubDate>Sun, 13 Sep 2015 15:13:32 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/6575/change-floating-window-move-step/</guid></item><item><title>Answer by Airblader for &lt;p&gt;I'd like to increase step of moving floating windows ($mod+shift+[ j k l ; ]), is there a way to do it without recompiling i3?&lt;/p&gt;
 </title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/6575/change-floating-window-move-step/?answer=6576#post-id-6576</link><description>See http://i3wm.org/docs/userguide.html#_focusing_moving_containers:

    move &lt;left|right|down|up&gt; [&lt;px&gt; px]

    Note that the amount of pixels you can specify for the move command is only relevant for floating containers. The default amount is 10 pixels.</description><pubDate>Sun, 13 Sep 2015 16:09:07 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/6575/change-floating-window-move-step/?answer=6576#post-id-6576</guid></item><item><title>Comment by Anon1234 for &lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href="http://i3wm.org/docs/userguide.html"&gt;http://i3wm.org/docs/userguide.html#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;focusing&lt;/em&gt;moving_containers:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;move &amp;lt;left|right|down|up&amp;gt; [&amp;lt;px&amp;gt; px]

Note that the amount of pixels you can specify for the move command is only relevant for floating containers. The default amount is 10 pixels.
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
</title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/6575/change-floating-window-move-step/?comment=6577#comment-6577</link><description>Thank you, i missed [&lt;px&gt; px] part when read the guide.</description><pubDate>Sun, 13 Sep 2015 16:31:34 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/6575/change-floating-window-move-step/?comment=6577#comment-6577</guid></item></channel></rss>